parameters:
Sakura: Well then, if the information
is correct, the Pink Snake gang's base
should be around here.

Sakura: What do you think, Rurika? My
intuition tells me that this one is a
hit.

Rurika: Yes, I agree. At first glance,
it looks like an abandoned old building,
but considering the security of this
area, it's too quiet.

Rurika: Since we know it's the Pink
Snake gang's base, the residents in the
area are too scared to approach.

Rurika: Logically, I speculate the
same.

Kenichi: We did it, Onee-san! Let's get
in there right away and crush them!!

Sakura: Oh, you seem to be full of
motivation.

Rurika: I'm counting on you, Kenichi-
san.

Kenichi: Y-Yeah! Watch me! I'm also a
member of the Future Special Police, you
know!

My name is Kenichi, I'm a trainee... of
the Special Police.

Actually, I'm not supposed to be
allowed due to my age. But because I was
compatible with the Future Special
Police's new equipment, the 'Bio Gear,'
they're letting me participate in
activities as a special case.

Sakura and Rurika are childhood friends.
It's a big deal that both of them have
agreed to take care of me.

Of course, Onee-chan and the others are
also Bio Gear compatible. They are
official members of the Future Special
Police, in other words, they're
incredibly strong.

Even with just the two of them, they
are capable of taking on ten or twenty
people.

Sakura is the one with red hair, Onee-
san.

As you can see, she has big breasts and
is beautiful. She gives off the vibe of
being a justice-loving hero who has
always hated dishonesty.

I was scolded a lot, or rather, I was
even hit. But in return, I was taken
care of a lot.

The one with blue hair is Rurika, Onee-
san.

As you can see, Sakura Onee-chan and I
are twin sisters. She has big breasts,
is beautiful, kind, and a bit cool.

I received help with my studies and she
cooked meals for me. She's not only
kind, but also strict at times. But,
after all, she took care of me a lot and
looked after me.

Both of them are beautiful... strong and
kind.
They are the best Onee-chans to me!

However, they are just too amazing... I
can't help but feel a little inferior.

Still, it's a concern that I'm still
seen as a 'little brother'...

When I was a kid, I could confidently
say that I would marry my Onee-chans...

I've been relying on them since a long
time ago, and even now they take care of
me as a trainee member. As a man, I
can't possibly say such things.

At the very least, I have to become a
full-fledged Future Special Police
officer. It would be embarrassing if I
couldn't become a man recognized by my
Onee-chans.
Therefore!

Now, I will do everything I can with
all my might!

To become a full-fledged Future Special
Police officer! In order to become a man
recognized by my Onee-chans!!

Kenichi: Wait for me, Pink Snake Gang!
I will definitely catch you!!

Sakura: Oh, nice spirit, Kenichi! Let's
get on board right away!

Sakura: Get pumped up and keep up with
me! Above all, a full-fledged Future
Special Police officer needs power!

Rurika: Honestly, Sakura, you're always
provoking him.

Rurika: It's great that you're
enthusiastic, Kenichi-san, but if you
want to become a full-fledged Future
Special Police officer, don't forget to
stay calm as well.
Kenichi: Y-Yes!
Not this way.
Not this way.
Not this way.
Alright... Let's go!!
